<h1>Workplace Injuries</h1>

<p>
Workplace injuries may develop from repetitive tasks, prolonged sitting, lifting,
or physically demanding work environments.
</p>

<p>
Chiropractic care supports recovery while emphasizing prevention and sustainable
return to work.
</p>

<h2>Common Workplace Injuries</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Low back strain</li>
  <li>Neck and shoulder tension</li>
  <li>Repetitive strain injuries</li>
</ul>

<h2>Care Approach</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Movement and ergonomic assessment</li>
  <li>Exercise-based rehabilitation</li>
  <li>Education for long-term injury prevention</li>
</ul>

